FBIS4-54331 "dreas103_d_94007" FBIS-EAS-94-103 Daily Report 26 May 1994 South Korea ROK Reacts to New Russia-DPRK Logging Agreement ROK Reacts to New Russia-DPRK Logging Agreement SK2705022394 Seoul SEOUL SINMUN in Korean 26 May 94 p 1 SK2705022394 Seoul SEOUL SINMUN Korean BFN [Text] Regarding the issue pertaining to new logging agreement reached between Russia and North Korea, a government official evaluated on 24 May that "the recent agreement stipulates the improved treatment of North Korean loggers. This is a stepped-up measure," and expressed that "however, the government will continue its efforts to further improve loggers' working conditions and their human rights."
